    BaseConverter<From,To>

    A bidirectional converter between String values and values of the given type.
    TwoWayConverter<From,To>
    The superinterface, Converter, converts values from type <From> to type <To> while this interface adds the ability to convert in the reverse direction from type <To> to type <From>.
